#. module: campus_employees
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campus_employees.employees_homepage_docs
msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-check-circle text-success me-2\"/> <strong>Action:</strong>"
" Admin selects the role from the <code>Academic Role</code> dropdown "
"(Lecturer / PMB Staff / Academic Staff) on the Job form. The system will use"
" this parameter as a logic indicator in the next steps."
msgstr "<i class=\"fa fa-check-circle text-success me-2\"/> <strong>Aksi:</strong> Admin memilih peran dari dropdown <code>Academic Role</code> (Lecturer / PMB Staff / Academic Staff) pada form Jabatan. Sistem akan menggunakan parameter ini sebagai indikator logika pada langkah berikutnya."

#. module: campus_employees
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campus_employees.employees_homepage_docs
msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-check-circle text-success me-2\"/> <strong>Action:</strong>"
" Open the *tab* <strong>PMB/Academic Jurisdiction</strong> on the employee "
"profile, then select the Faculty or Study Program that is within their work "
"scope. Odoo will lock data access according to those territory limits."
msgstr "<i class=\"fa fa-check-circle text-success me-2\"/> <strong>Aksi:</strong> Buka *tab* <strong>PMB/Academic Jurisdiction</strong> pada profil pegawai, lalu pilih Fakultas atau Program Studi yang berada dalam ruang lingkup kerjanya. Odoo akan mengunci akses data sesuai batas wilayah tersebut."

#. module: campus_employees
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campus_employees.employees_homepage_docs
msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-check-circle text-success me-2\"/> <strong>Action:</strong>"
" Staff fills in the biodata, uploads photos, and determines the "
"department/faculty the employee belongs to."
msgstr "<i class=\"fa fa-check-circle text-success me-2\"/> <strong>Aksi:</strong> Staf mengisi biodata, mengunggah foto, dan menentukan departemen/fakultas asal pegawai tersebut."

#. module: campus_employees
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campus_employees.employees_homepage_docs
msgid "<i class=\"fa fa-lock text-success me-2\"/>Security Jurisdictions"
msgstr "<i class=\"fa fa-lock text-success me-2\"/>Yurisdiksi Keamanan"

#. module: campus_employees
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campus_employees.employees_homepage_docs
msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-magic text-dark me-2\"/> <strong>UI Automation:</strong> "
"When staff selects a job position that has the \"Lecturer\" role, the "
"academic profile *Tab* will appear. If the job role is \"PMB Staff\" or "
"\"Academic Staff\", the relevant jurisdiction *Tab* will appear. This form "
"is highly dynamic!"
msgstr "<i class=\"fa fa-magic text-dark me-2\"/> <strong>Otomatisasi UI:</strong> Saat staf memilih posisi pekerjaan yang memiliki peran \"Lecturer\", *Tab* profil akademik akan muncul. Jika peran jabatannya adalah \"PMB Staff\" atau \"Academic Staff\", *Tab* yurisdiksi yang relevan akan muncul. Formulir ini sangat dinamis!"

#. module: campus_employees
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campus_employees.employees_homepage_docs
msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-shield text-danger me-2\"/> <strong>Strict "
"Security:</strong> Without a clear jurisdiction, faculty-level staff risk "
"viewing/modifying confidential data of other faculties."
msgstr "<i class=\"fa fa-shield text-danger me-2\"/> <strong>Keamanan Ketat:</strong> Tanpa yurisdiksi yang jelas, staf tingkat fakultas berisiko melihat/mengubah data rahasia fakultas lain."

